---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Funeral Planning Guide">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Funeral Planning Guide</h1>
    
    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
      <h2>Steps to Plan a Funeral in Houston</h2>
      
      <h3>1. Immediate Steps</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact the deceased's doctor or emergency services</li>
        <li>Notify immediate family members</li>
        <li>Contact a funeral home</li>
        <li>Obtain death certificate</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2. Funeral Arrangements</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Choose burial or cremation</li>
        <li>Select a casket or urn</li>
        <li>Plan the service details</li>
        <li>Choose location and time</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>3. Documentation</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Death certificates (multiple copies)</li>
        <li>Insurance policies</li>
        <li>Military discharge papers (if applicable)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>4. Additional Considerations</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Religious or cultural requirements</li>
        <li>Memorial service options</li>
        <li>Reception planning</li>
        <li>Obituary preparation</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
        <h3>Need Immediate Assistance?</h3>
        <p>Call us at (123) 456-7890 for help with funeral planning.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>